Package: cvMAGIC
Title: MAGIC-CLoR: Calibrated Association Scoring after MAGIC Diffusion
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Author: Annice Najafi [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Annice Najafi <annicenajafi27@gmail.com>
Description: Native R implementation of MAGIC (Markov Affinity-based Graph
    Imputation of Cells, van Dijk et al. 2018) together with MAGIC-CLoR, a
    parameter-free Context Likelihood of Relatedness (CLR) calibration of the
    post-diffusion correlation readout that improves transcription-factor
    target recovery. Also provides Batson-style molecular cross-validation for
    diffusion-time selection, per-gene and per-module adaptive variants, and
    bootstrap per-(cell, gene) standard errors.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports:
    Matrix,
    RANN,
    irlba,
    stats
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
